Author: WORDCOIN
Title: [ANN]🔵🌟WORDCOIN🌟🔵ICO finished!🌟Platform for copywriters&translators
Body: Today is the last day of WORDCOIN PRE ICO, and we’d like to inform you about the last chance to buy WORDCOIN for a really low price! We’d like to thank our investors, who helped us to collect funds for word.expert preparations and a huge PR campaign before ICO starts! Very soon it will start working and the more and more users will join it! We believe that after word.expert start, WORDCOIN rate will rapidly grow because of its limited offer and high demand of the provided services (content writing, translation, proofreading by native speakers and etc.). We expect its increase in 20 times within 9 months, as the platform will be very attractive both for freelancers and companies because of the lack of agent fees, multiplier effect of combined services and so on. All of the PRE ICO tokens will be distributed after PRE ICO closure, and there are 22 hours left to become our investor! If you still have no understanding about our project idea, you can check our website www.wordcoin.io. If you’re interested in making contributions to WORDCOIN, the instructions how to invest is available by the link: https://my.wordcoin.io/instruction.pdf . Besides all the rumours, we’re full of power to make our idea real and believe in our project success! Best wishes to everyone! And remember: “In the beginning was the WORD”!

Author: laurenB7742
Title: [ANN]🔵🌟WORDCOIN🌟🔵ICO finished!🌟Platform for copywriters&translators
Body: I don't understand this. How can you guarantee that 1 WORD = 1 $ or more?? It says in your whitepaper: The starting exchange rates for WORDCOIN will be set at the pre-ICO, where 2,000,000 coins will be sold out. The amount of the funds, raised at the pre-ICO will be divided by 2 million WORDCOINs, enabling to determine the USD-denominated exchange rate.  Ok so let's say you will raise around 50 000 USD during the ICO and you will distribute all 2 000 000 coins to investors. Clearly, the price of 1 WORD will be less than 1 USD, it will be 0.025 USD. You would need to raise 2 million USD or more to guarantee the minimum price of $1 per WORD.  How many coins are there and are they ERC20 tokens? Total number of coins in pre-ICO, ICO and post-ICO is 9 900 000 which is quite low number so the price could actually reach 1 USD and more, but it is confusing because you will give 2 million coins to investors who will invest much less than 2 million USD.

Author: WORDCOIN
Title: [ANN]🔵🌟WORDCOIN🌟🔵ICO finished!🌟Platform for copywriters&translators
Body: We organize PRE ICO to raise funds for marketing campaign and to prepare a working platform before ICO start. During the ICO, the price for 1 wordcoin will start from 1 USD. We'll sell 7 000 000 tokens during the ICO, and they are ERC20 tokens  The rate growth will start, when the more and more users will start using the platform. As the number of tokens is limited and the services are in high demand (considering platform numerous advantages), in 9 months, when the platform will be very popular, the rate will be very high.

Author: WORDCOIN
Title: [ANN]🔵🌟WORDCOIN🌟🔵ICO finished!🌟Platform for copywriters&translators
Body: Why PRE ICO step is the most profitable for contributions to WORDCOIN: 1. During PRE ICO we collect funds for development of the future platform WORD.EXPERT and for marketing expenses during ICO. That’s why during ICO we’ll show the platform and hold a tremendous PR campaign. The interest to WORDCOIN will increase and its minimum price will start from $1. 2. WORDCOIN cost during PRE ICO is much cheaper. During this stage its exchange rate into dollars will be defined, counted by the total contributions amount/2 000 000 WORDCOIN. At first day of PRE ICO the exchange rate of WORDCOIN reached 2 cents. That’s 50 times less than initial rate of WORDCOIN during ICO stage. 3. 2 000 000 WORDCOINs will be automatically distributed between all investors of PRE ICO in accordance with smart contract conditions.  This means that during PRE ICO investors will receive a large amount of WORDCOINs, which price is much lower than 1$ 4. As the finalized version of WORDCOIN will be presented and more tremendous PR campaign will be organized at ICO stage, we plan to attract the main part of contributions during it. By the way, all the PRE ICO participants will receive 3% from the contributed funds at ICO, which will be distributed proportionally to their invested amount.  5. We can’t influence all the mentioned activities, as they’re totally automated and are locked into smart-contracts. Investors receive all bonuses and transfers in a decentralized way according to smart contracts conditions. The contract is posted on GitHub, and everyone can check its details and understand that all the contributions are secure and profitable.

Author: WORDCOIN
Title: [ANN]🔵🌟WORDCOIN🌟🔵ICO finished!🌟Platform for copywriters&translators
Body: Hi, Thanks for your opinion! We have a few points to think in a different way. Why? Because there're no similar freelance platforms in the world, which can provide such a multiplyer effect, as ours. For example, there're lots of translation services, but to proofread it, you have to find an additional resource. To post the translated article on the controlled websites, you need to order service in the third place. And the total comission can be really significant! Our platform combines all these services in one place, users don't have to waste time on registration on many resources, they'll get the needed cumulative result on the same platform! That fact automatically excludes PR agencies fees, which can reach 60% of order price. It's not profitable for companies to register on a few resources, they'd better use PR agencies services and overpay.   Our future users will already get their rating before entering Word Expert platform (I mean current bounty participants). Newly-registred users will also get bonuses for registration! The addtional advantage is that the problem of international transactions and currency convertation will be solved. WORDCOIN has no limits and doesn't depend on legislation of different countries. This fact and the fact, that there will be translation options into more than 60 languages, will make Word Expert more attractive on the global level and no similar platforms in the world can provide the same advantages!

If your link is used by investors, you’ll get 10% from their referrals, 3% from a referral of the second level, 1% - from the third level and so on. All the bonuses will be paid in ETH. For those, who still haven’t registered, do not hesitate to get your bonuses!

Author: WORDCOIN
Title: [ANN]🔵🌟WORDCOIN🌟🔵ICO finished!🌟Platform for copywriters&translators
Body: Hello, thanks for your important question! We accept that there're many similar ICO projects on the market, but regarding Blocklancer and BitJob we still have found a few significant differencies:  Bitjob  Bitjob is a really great project, but it has a few differences from us: - it's aimed to students market, which is very narrow; - student don't have enough experience for implementing many kinds of works, reducing the number of clients; - it's possible to use both tokens and fiat money on their platform, leading to insufficient demand of token, which influences its rate growth.  Our platform combines complimentary freelance services with the market volume more than 1 trillion dollars. And the only payment method will be WORDCOIN, issued in 100% amount. Because of its decentralization, WE platform excludes agents' fees and resource owners profit with the help of smart contracts. That's why clients pay less, and authors earn more (at least +30%). This fact and an active PR campaign will allow to attract 10 million users within 1 year. Taking into account WORDCOIN rate will grow 150 times.  Blocklancer - In Blocklancer project a token is a share in the company, in WORDCOIN it is the cryptocurrency, supplied with services; - Blocklancer platform has the possibility for centralization, WORDCOIN is totally decentralized platrform; - In Blockchainer docs it's not mentioned which freelance services will be provided (in which field, I mean), WORDCOIN mentions the field and the services, which provide multiplier effect, being combined together. WORDCOIN team has experience in the providing the mentioned services around 12 years; - In Blocklancer token owners can take part in disputes between clients and authors, WORDCOIN uses rating and review system, which will not waste the time of our token owners and let the argument being resolved between two parties (clients and authors).  - In Blocklancer it's not clear whether the services will be provided globally, In WORDCOIN the services will be avaiable in more than 20 languages. - In Blocklancer investors may be interested in getting profit from 3% comissions, in WORDCOIN case the investors can predict the rapid growth of WORDCOIN rate, as more and more users will keep joining the platform, and it will become more and more popular.  Both projects are really nice, we hope them all the best!
